---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About | Beyond All Maps"
  description="Learn more about Beyond All Maps and the documentary travel photography project by Thorsten Mehret."
>

<section class="about-hero">

  <div class="about-overlay">

    <p class="eyebrow">
  ABOUT
</p>

<h1>
  Beyond All Maps
</h1>

<p class="subtitle">
  A long-term documentary photography project
</p>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="about-content">

  <div class="text-block">

    <h2>The Project</h2>

    <p>
      Beyond All Maps is my long-term documentary travel photography project
      dedicated to portraying our planet through authentic encounters, extraordinary
      landscapes, wildlife and diverse cultures.
    </p>

    <p>
      Rather than collecting destinations, the goal is to create visual stories
      that capture the unique identity of every place.
    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="quote-section">

  <div class="quote-content">

    <p class="quote-text">
      A lifelong journey to document the diversity of our planet.
    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="about-content">

  <div class="text-block">

    <h2>Why I Travel</h2>

    <p>
      I have never travelled to collect countries or to tick destinations off a
      list. Every journey begins with curiosity — a desire to understand how
      people live, how landscapes shape cultures and how wildlife survives in
      some of the world's most extraordinary places.
    </p>

    <p>
      Photography allows me to preserve these moments and to share them as
      visual stories. Some places are breathtaking, others are challenging, but
      every destination has something unique to reveal.
    </p>

    <p>
      Beyond All Maps is my attempt to create an authentic portrait of our
      planet — one journey, one story and one photograph at a time.
    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="about-content alt-section">

  <div class="text-block">

    <h2>What You'll Find</h2>

    <p>
      Every destination featured on Beyond All Maps is presented through
      carefully curated travel stories and photography that go beyond the
      obvious.
    </p>

    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>Authentic documentary travel photography</li>
      <li>In-depth travel stories and itineraries</li>
      <li>Wildlife, landscapes and remote places</li>
      <li>People, cultures and everyday life</li>
      <li>Travel inspiration from every corner of the world</li>
    </ul>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="stats-section">

  <div class="stats-intro">

    <h2>By the Numbers</h2>

    <p>
      Beyond All Maps is an ongoing long-term project that continues to grow
      with every new journey.
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="stats-grid">

    <div class="stat">
      <h3>140+</h3>
      <p>Countries Visited</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stat">
      <h3>90+</h3>
      <p>Covered in ...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stat">
      <h3>70+</h3>
      <p>... Photo Stories</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stat">
      <h3>1</h3>
      <p>Long-Term Project</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<section class="about-cta">

  <div class="about-cta-content">

    <h2>Start Exploring</h2>

    <p>
      Every journey begins with curiosity. Discover documentary travel
      photography, authentic travel stories and remarkable places from around
      the world.
    </p>

    <div class="intro-buttons">

      <a
        class="button-primary"
        href="https://beyondallmaps.exposure.co/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Explore Photo Stories
      </a>

      <a
        class="button-secondary"
        href="https://de.pinterest.com/BeyondAllMaps/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Follow on Pinterest
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <p>© 2026 · Beyond All Maps</p>
</footer>

</MainLayout>